imdb.plot outline: Amber is a model turned actress who philosophizes about life, love and the daily struggles of an indie actress. After landing a hosting gig for the haunted travel show "Florida in the Shadows", Amber discovers her dream job might actually be a nightmare!
imdb.title: Amber in the Shadows
plot: The video diary of an aspiring actress who finds more than she bargained for on the set of a haunted travel show.::Bruce Wood
